---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Pixel8 Multimedia privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal data."
>
  <section class="relative bg-bg-secondary py-16">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-pop-orange"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 font-dm text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-pop-orange transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-off-white">Privacy Policy</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="font-montserrat font-bold text-5xl text-off-white tracking-wide mb-4" style="text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4);">PRIVACY POLICY</h1>
      <p class="font-dm text-gray-400 text-sm">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="space-y-8 font-dm text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Pixel8 Multimedia is a UK-based wall art brand. Our website address is https://pixel8multimedia.co.uk. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your personal data responsibly.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">What Data We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">When you place an order or contact us, we may collect the following information:</p>
        <p>Your name, email address, shipping address, phone number (if provided), payment information (processed securely by Stripe — we do not store card details), photographs you upload for personalised orders, and any messages or instructions you provide. We also collect basic analytics data through cookies to understand how visitors use our site.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>We use your personal data to process and fulfil your orders, send order confirmations and dispatch notifications, create personalised artwork based on photos you provide, respond to your enquiries, improve our website and services, and send marketing emails (only if you've opted in via our newsletter). We will never sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Payment Processing</h2>
        <p>All payments are processed securely through Stripe. We do not store or have access to your full card details. Stripe's privacy policy can be found at stripe.com/privacy.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Photos & Personalised Orders</h2>
        <p>When you upload photos for personalised orders, these are stored securely and used solely for the purpose of creating your artwork. We may retain your photos for a reasonable period after order completion in case of reprints or quality issues. We will never use your photos for marketing without your explicit consent.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses cookies to maintain your shopping cart, remember your preferences, and analyse site traffic. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to access the personal data we hold about you, request correction or deletion of your data, object to processing of your data, and request a copy of your data in a portable format. To exercise any of these rights, please contact us via our contact page.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy-related questions, please <a href="/contact" class="text-pixel-cyan hover:text-pop-orange transition-colors">contact us</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
